Separability measures¶

For a cloud with tokens from all types.

The functions can be interpreted as follows: {measure}_[tokvecs/clouds](class), with tokvecs/clouds indicating whether the measure was applied to the token matrix before or after MDS.

Index

  • Distance Ratio
  • Silhouette
  • Same Class Paths
  • Same Class Items among k Nearest neighbours
